n的各种笔记写作软件bear Ulysses mweb……<br>win和Android上我就不清楚了<br>notion也行 是全平台的 就是感觉有点卡<br>有iPad/mac的话可以用MarginNote 专门整理读书笔记画思维导图<br>Simplenote也可以试试看","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/36/06/360675.jpg","floor":"#8","id":"1452323","time":"2019-6-10 17:34","userId":"blackadder","userName":"Blackadder","userSign":"(In libris libertas.)","message":"Goodnotes和Notability","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/43/06/430610.jpg","floor":"#9","id":"1452789","time":"2019-6-11 22:55","userId":"430610","userName":"绯色Ace","userSign":"(We always keep minority spirit)","message":"markdown搭配git可以保持最高的稳定性，毕竟git不用出服务器钱嘛<br>移动端的markdown也有MarkdownX和JotterPad X这样的","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/99/299900.jpg","floor":"#10","id":"1452794","time":"2019-6-11 23:04","userId":"299900","userName":"Oshino","userSign":"","message":"只有我用纸笔吗<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/26/63/266388.jpg","floor":"#10-1","id":"1452944","time":"2019-6-12 10:48","userId":"266388","userName":"恋花绽放樱飞时","userSign":"","message":"你不是一个人！<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/14/36/143677.jpg","floor":"#11","id":"1452810","time":"2019-6-11 23:33","userId":"gameswordsman","userName":"游侠GS","userSign":"(明日やろうは馬鹿野郎だ)","message":"印象笔记+Google Keep，复杂+简单，就是后者要魔法上网。<br>印象笔记现在支持Markdown了，稍微学下解决排版问题。普通的笔记还是会出现多平台同步后格式难看...<br>关键还是要定期整理，至少分“TODO”、“Current当前”、“Archive归档”几种对应不同需要的笔记本。<br>围绕“笔记本”和“标签”的各种花式用法初看很头疼，用习惯了还是挺香的。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/28/76/287622.jpg","floor":"#12","id":"1452811","time":"2019-6-11 23:40","userId":"trim21","userName":"Trim21","userSign":"(异端比异教徒更可恨)","message":"onenote在16年某次更新之后结构太复杂了，在具体到某篇文章之前要划好几次，就换别的笔记了。现在在用滴答清单当todo+笔记","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/99/139922.jpg","floor":"#12-1","id":"1453758","time":"2019-6-14 07:31","userId":"hashireowl","userName":"owl","userSign":"","message":"对...分太多层级我这种老年人划着划着就忘记该干啥了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/14/131492.jpg","floor":"#13","id":"1452854","time":"2019-6-12 02:39","userId":"misakaxindex","userName":"東瀬まつり太","userSign":"([s]安静点格子[/s])","message":"onenote选手<br>用alt+ctrl+1/2/3/4/5/6调节标题 副标题 副副标题 强调等<br>[tab]调整缩进<br>[* ][空格 ]列表<br>uwp和安卓间onenote同步从来没有过排版混乱的问题","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/76/277679.jpg","floor":"#13-1","id":"1453763","time":"2019-6-14 08:28","userId":"jaeycin","userName":"三木森","userSign":"","message":"附议！"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/87/278708.jpg","floor":"#14","id":"1453737","time":"2019-6-14 00:57","userId":"tanimodori","userName":"谷戻り","userSign":"(そして、谷から戻る。)","message":"Tiddlywiki5<br>+ Markdown，HTML<br>+ 一些好用的插件：KaTeX，Highlight.js<br>+ 条目控制，Tag<br>+ 一定的脚本语法<br>+ 便携性，备份方便<br>- 要自己折腾样式、脚本、etc<br>- 版本控制<br>- 跨平台麻烦，要自己Host服务器<br>- 多用户权限控制<br>- 没有手写/平板支持","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/04/97/49777.jpg","floor":"#15","id":"1453748","time":"2019-6-14 05:37","userId":"bgmouse","userName":"MousHu","userSign":"(miaow~~~)","message":"纸质笔记本有时候写起来很有感觉 ...<br>OneNote 有段时间使用强度挺高的 ...<br>配上手机随便用用的临时便签或小纸质本<br>加上电脑上的文件夹文件结构 ... <br>至今基本就这几样看情况使用了 ...<br><br>不过整理是什么 ... <br>一般再查阅到的时候 可能会引用下 或者直接更新下 ...<br>不知道以后有没有这么规整的需求 ...<br><br>不过自己做的东西 不管用什么方法在什么地方 <br>一般也都有些条条框框 ...<br>现阶段自己感觉还行的样子？","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/99/139922.jpg","floor":"#16","id":"1453759","time":"2019-6-14 07:32","userId":"hashireowl","userName":"owl","userSign":"(素晴らしい作品の感動を共有して何が悪い! ... ... .. ...)","message":"现在就用markdown加蹭GitHub<br>不过以后估计会传不少图片，唉...","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/02/35/23570.jpg","floor":"#17","id":"1453765","time":"2019-6-14 08:43","userId":"htsune_miku","userName":"Jadeity","userSign":"(明天，我就要去屠龙（失恋了，不想再屠龙了） ...)","message":"搭车求能macOS和android之间同步的笔记或者文件管理软件，就像iCloud那样，电脑编辑完出门手机就能继续看或编辑，不用刻意点同步按钮或等待一段时间同步，有变化立即同步那种。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/04/210454.jpg","floor":"#17-1","id":"1453767","time":"2019-6-14 08:47","userId":"mp4spig","userName":"🌸九重凛🌸","userSign":"","message":"notion啊"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/48/00/480062.jpg","floor":"#17-2","id":"1455870","time":"2019-6-21 09:40","userId":"480062","userName":"Hydsiun","userSign":"","message":"印象笔记就可"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/84/408455.jpg","floor":"#18","id":"1456032","time":"2019-6-21 17:08","userId":"sakinin","userName":"三一咲忍","userSign":"(邦邦人)","message":"mark","sub":[]}]